components.templateData:
<ion-header>

	<ion-toolbar mode="ios" class="header__wrapper">
		<ion-buttons slot="secondary" *ngIf="buttons && buttons.left">
			<app-custom-icon-button
				*ngFor="let button of buttons.left"
				[name]="button"
				size="24px"
			></app-custom-icon-button>
		</ion-buttons>
		<ion-buttons slot="primary" *ngIf="buttons && buttons.right">
			<app-custom-icon-button
				*ngFor="let button of buttons.right"
				[name]="button"
				size="24px"
			></app-custom-icon-button>
		</ion-buttons>
		<ion-title class="header__title">{{title}}</ion-title>
	</ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

components.name: TabsPage
components.templateData:
<ion-header *ngIf="config.header">
  <ion-toolbar>
    <ion-title>tabs</ion-title>
  </ion-toolbar>
</ion-header>

<ion-content>
  <ion-tabs>
    <ion-tab-bar slot="bottom">
      <ion-tab-button tab="{{t.tab}}" *ngFor="let t of config.tabs">
        <ion-icon name="{{t.icon}}" *ngIf="t.icon"></ion-icon>
        <ion-label *ngIf="t.label">{{t.label}}</ion-label>
      </ion-tab-button>
    </ion-tab-bar>
  </ion-tabs>
</ion-content>
